    "Html": "<p>Hi, nobody answered me so I have had to figure it by myself. To have the behavior I wanted for the ribbon buttons&nbsp;I ended replacing the button object from scratch using the next code:</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:navy\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\">Key</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;RibbonStyle&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> TargetType</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> r</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\">RibbonButton</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\"> }&quot;&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;BorderBrush&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> Value</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;Transparent&quot; /&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;BorderThickness&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> Value</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;Template&quot;&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Setter.Value</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">ControlTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Grid</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515\">Border</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:blue\">=&quot;LightBorder&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:red\"> CornerRadius</span><span style=\"font-si